      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. but i feel like when people say \"fake news\" it's not always the same thing. sometimes they're talking about actual lies, but other times it feels like politicians just use the term whenever they don't like a story that's actually true. do you think the term itself is being used as a tool to dismiss things people don't want to hear?",
